summary: The movie Immortals inspired me to \"try\" and create the beautiful Isabel Lucas in the world of skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Level 1 Imperial - Helgen Keep

This is my first time making a character based off of someone in real life so get off me, I know it looks nothing like her.

Installation:

Drag the .ess file to you skyrim saves directory (My Documents>My Games>Skyrim>Saves)

I used \"lovely hairstyles\" by snoop to get the hair like that.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7403
author: Andrew Siems
